OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1777054266
OL,3,CResidents protest against the
OL,4,Ctemporary closure of their leisure
OL,5,Ccentre
OL,7,FPeople living on an estate in the
OL,8,Fheart of the City of London have been
OL,9,Fdemonstrating against the temporary
OL,10,Fclosure of their leisure center today
OL,11,F- the only publicly funded one in the
OL,12,FSquare Mile.
OL,14,FThe Golden Lane Sports and Fitness
OL,15,FCentre has been part of the housing
OL,16,Festate since the 1950s but the charity
OL,17,Fwhich runs it, Fusion Lifestyle, has
OL,18,Fgone into administrations.
OL,20,FCampaigners want the City of London
OL,21,FCorporation to secure its future.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/10
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,406,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1777054266
OL,3,CResidents protest against the
OL,4,Ctemporary closure of their leisure
OL,5,Ccentre
OL,7,FThe centre serves the whole community,
OL,8,Fincluding SEND children, elderly
OL,9,Fresidents and GP-referred cardiac
OL,10,Fpatients.
OL,12,FOne user said: "I had a cardiac arrest
OL,13,Fa couple of years ago, Golden Lane has
OL,14,Fbeen really important to my rehab.
OL,16,F"I don't think I can find equivalent
OL,17,Ffacilities elsewhere without
OL,18,Ftravelling the distance. It's not just
OL,19,Fdoing the sports, it's the community."
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/10
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,406,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1777054266
OL,3,CResidents protest against the
OL,4,Ctemporary closure of their leisure
OL,5,Ccentre
OL,7,FShe continued: "Different groups have
OL,8,Fall been there for years. Yes, we can
OL,9,Fgo elsewhere but we're going to
OL,10,Fcompletely lose that community.
OL,12,F"It's going to break it up and that's
OL,13,Fthe saddest thing of all."
OL,15,FRoger, is another leisure centre user.
OL,16,FHe said:
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/10
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,406,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1777054266
OL,3,CResidents protest against the
OL,4,Ctemporary closure of their leisure
OL,5,Ccentre
OL,7,F"I have lessons there twice a week. I
OL,8,Fhave a swimming lesson, I have a gym
OL,9,Flesson. Then I go to another swimming
OL,10,Flesson to remember what I'm being
OL,11,Ftaught to do.
OL,13,F"I live in the Barbican. It's right at
OL,14,Fthe core of the community. It's lovely
OL,15,Fdoing it with other people that you
OL,16,Frecognise and know."
OL,18,FThe City of London Corporation want to
OL,19,F"reassure Londoners" about the future
OL,20,Fof the leisure centre.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/10
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,406,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1777054266
OL,3,CResidents protest against the
OL,4,Ctemporary closure of their leisure
OL,5,Ccentre
OL,7,FThe chair of the Court of Common
OL,8,FCouncil, Helen Fentimen said:
OL,10,F"The City of London Corporation
OL,11,Fremains fully committed to the
OL,12,Finvestment of a #10.4 million
OL,13,Frefurbishment programme which will
OL,14,Fsecure a modern high quality leisure
OL,15,Fcentre for the long term."
OL,17,FShe added that the closure of the
OL,18,Fcentre "is earlier than usual," and
OL,19,Frecognised "the disruption this has
OL,20,Fcaused."
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/10
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,406,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1777054266
OL,3,CResidents protest against the
OL,4,Ctemporary closure of their leisure
OL,5,Ccentre
OL,7,FHelen continued:
OL,9,F"However, we have been focused, since
OL,10,Flearning about the administration of
OL,11,FFusion, on putting new alternative
OL,12,Fservices in place at a very rapid pace.
OL,14,F" We have done that and all service
OL,15,Fusers have got alternatives put in
OL,16,Fplace for them, within a ten minute
OL,17,Fdistance of the leisure centre."
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/10
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,406,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1777054266
OL,3,CResidents protest against the
OL,4,Ctemporary closure of their leisure
OL,5,Ccentre
OL,7,FThe City of London Corporation added
OL,8,Fthat a survey it carried out, with
OL,9,Fover 400 people, found the biggest
OL,10,Fbarrier stopping respondents from
OL,11,Fexercising was the quality of the
OL,12,Fcentre.
OL,14,FRajesh Thind is a spokesperson for the
OL,15,Fcampaigners. He said there needs to be
OL,16,Fmore collaboration with the community.
OL,18,FRajesh told ITV News London that:
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/10
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,406,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1777054266
OL,3,CResidents protest against the
OL,4,Ctemporary closure of their leisure
OL,5,Ccentre
OL,7,F"Going forward we've submitted an
OL,8,Finterim proposal for how we think we
OL,9,Fcan work in the partnership with the
OL,10,FCity of London Corporation.
OL,12,F"Both in keeping the centre open and
OL,13,Fmaking sure that when the consultation
OL,14,Fdoes happen it is done with proper
OL,15,Fconsultation and codesign with the
OL,16,Fcommunity.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G8/10
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,406,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1777054266
OL,3,CResidents protest against the
OL,4,Ctemporary closure of their leisure
OL,5,Ccentre
OL,7,F"To make sure Golden Lane continues to
OL,8,Fthrive, rather than being the subject
OL,9,Fof more of the neglect, disdain and
OL,10,Flack of proper consultation that I'm
OL,11,Fvery sorry to say has been the pattern
OL,12,Fover the last seven years."
OL,14,FRajesh continued:
OL,16,F"They (the City of London Corporation)
OL,17,Fdidn't expect to get any push back,
OL,18,Fthey thought they could just close the
OL,19,Fcentre without any proper feedback
OL,20,Ffrom us.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G9/10
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,406,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40510
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1777054266
OL,3,CResidents protest against the
OL,4,Ctemporary closure of their leisure
OL,5,Ccentre
OL,7,F"That is just not going to stand with
OL,8,Four community."
OL,10,FResidents are waiting to hear more
OL,11,Fabout the future of Golden Lane
OL,12,FLeisure Centre.
OL,14,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,15,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,16,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,17,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,18,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,19,Fbelow...
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G10/10
